text: Weichs is a municipality in Dachau, a district (Landkreis) in Upper Bavaria. There are 4 main villages in Weichs - Weichs, Aufhausen, Ebersbach, and Fränking. There are several smaller villages: Albertshof, Biechlhof, Breitenwiesen, Daxberg, Edenholzhausen, Edenpfaffenhofen, Erlbach, Erlhausen, Hölzböck, Jedenhofen, and Zillhofen. == References == Category:Dachau (district)
title: Weichs
